    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eversiege is a game where you have to find balance between your production and building defense to survive waves of enemies. Each siege defended provides experience that can be later spend on unlocking new buildings, leaders and upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PRODUCTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Establish good economy by placing production buildings that'll give you various resources needed for further constructions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/2b7e38d82bebf8aa4927ed12204b365a.poster.avif?t=1762272688\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/2b7e38d82bebf8aa4927ed12204b365a.webm?t=1762272688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/2b7e38d82bebf8aa4927ed12204b365a.mp4?t=1762272688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEFENSE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build defenses to protect your city from enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/71212f6710f6c25f6aff6f3d9fa96888.poster.avif?t=1762272688\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/71212f6710f6c25f6aff6f3d9fa96888.webm?t=1762272688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/71212f6710f6c25f6aff6f3d9fa96888.mp4?t=1762272688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REST</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you survive until the night, you will have some time to recover and prepare for further fights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/77df4f4c6274cd02139458f69aa230e4.poster.avif?t=1762272688\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/77df4f4c6274cd02139458f69aa230e4.webm?t=1762272688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/77df4f4c6274cd02139458f69aa230e4.mp4?t=1762272688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAN YOUR NEXT MOVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the siege ends, you'll need to decide which path to choose next. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/b504c2b94366b1cfa4ba4cc1f3f500bc.poster.avif?t=1762272688\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/b504c2b94366b1cfa4ba4cc1f3f500bc.webm?t=1762272688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/b504c2b94366b1cfa4ba4cc1f3f500bc.mp4?t=1762272688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEFEND, DEFEND, LOSE... REPEAT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even defeat won't stop you from trying again and again. But each siege is different thanks to procedurally generated levels!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/97d4c180e8cb1474ee80ed494d087b5f.poster.avif?t=1762272688\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018990/extras/97d4c180e8cb1474ee80ed494d087b5f.webm?t=1762272688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
